highlights:
Pros:
- Outperforms OpenAI’s GPT-4 across a range of text, image, coding, and reasoning benchmarks :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}
- Natively understands and reasons across sequences of text, images, audio, and video :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}
- Integrates into Gmail, Docs, Slides, and Sheets via Duet AI for enhanced productivity :contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}
